[SN]TITLE[SN]
United Airlines: Eyewitness on how passenger was dragged off plane

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
United Airlines has been severely criticised after a passenger was forcibly ejected by airport security staff from one of its flights, after no one volunteered to leave the plane.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
11 April 2017 Last updated at 16:32 BST
The passenger who was sitting next to the man taken off the flight told BBC 5 Live radio that the 69-year-old was "dragged off" the plane.
She said that the officer was "very direct with his words".
This clip is originally from 5 live Phil Williams on Monday 10 April 2017
